# Frontend Conventions

## Stack

- **Build**: Vite + `vite-plugin-glsl` for GLSL imports
- **3D**: Raw Three.js (no R3F / TresJS) — direct control of render loop, ShaderMaterial, BufferAttribute
- **UI**: React DOM overlay (HUD layer) — Tooltip, Drawer, Loading, Timeline
- **State bridge**: Zustand — Three.js writes selection/hover state, React reads; React writes navigation commands, Three.js executes

## TypeScript

- Strict mode enabled
- JSON schema types from Tech Spec §4 defined in `frontend/src/types/`

## Rendering Architecture

- **Macro layer**: `THREE.Points` + custom ShaderMaterial (1 draw call for ~60K particles)
  - **P6.2.2**: Single opaque pass (`transparent: false`, `depthWrite: true`) — circular points with a one-line `smoothstep` edge only (no halo / Bloom in the default path).
  - Vertex: position, size (log vote_count), `color` (genres[0] palette sRGB), `voteNorm` (`vote_average / 10`); Z-slab drives **size only** via `uActiveSizeMul` / `uBgSizeMul`. Color is recomputed in the vertex shader from palette hue in OKLab + lightness from `voteNorm` + fixed chroma (`uLMin` / `uLMax` / `uChroma`).
  - Fragment: flat `vColor` + circle discard + minimal AA.
- **Selected layer**: IcoSphere + Perlin Noise ShaderMaterial (on-demand per click); visibility toggles with selection fly-to (no macro opacity ramp).
- **Post-processing**: `EffectComposer` + `UnrealBloomPass` are **constructed but not attached** by default; the render loop uses `renderer.render(scene, camera)` with `renderer.outputColorSpace = THREE.SRGBColorSpace`. Call `window.__bloom.enable()` to attach the pass and switch to `composer.render()` (revive / polish).

## Camera

- Axis always parallel to Z (no rotation/tilt)
- Scroll: Z-axis travel (time depth)
- Drag: truck (horizontal) + pedestal (vertical) only
- Click-select: smooth fly-to (600–800ms easeOutCubic), axis stays parallel

## Interaction (P6.3.1)

- **Hover / click（Points 路径）**：**屏幕空间圆盘**与 `point.vert.glsl` 的 `gl_PointSize` **1:1** — `computePointScreenRadiusCss`；改点大小或 `uSizeScale` / `uActiveSizeMul` 须同步改 TS。
- **Hover / click（P8.4 dual `InstancedMesh`）**：`interaction.ts` 用 **ray–world-sphere**（半径与 `galaxyActive.vert` 的 `sActive` 一致），不用 `Raycaster.intersectObject` 做主判定（引擎射线忽略顶点 `sActive` 缩放）。Click 仍带 `inFocus > 0.5` slab 门控。

## Data Loading

- Default: `galaxy_data.json.gz` fetched at startup (`import.meta.env.BASE_URL` + `data/...`); gzip magic vs HTTP-transparent gzip handled in `frontend/src/data/loadGalaxyGzip.ts`; full-screen loading + optional progress until parsed
- Split into GPU BufferAttributes + DOM HUD data after parse
